{"schema_version": "1.0", "decision_id": "FD-20260713-HARDENING", "title": "APPROVE_HELM_AUTONOMOUS_HARDENING (scoped, local-only)", "status": "RATIFIED", "authority": "FOUNDER", "scope": {"factory_ids": ["HASF", "HRF", "HCF", "HSF", "HMF"], "product_ids": ["*"], "mission_ids": ["HELM_HARDENING"], "environments": ["local"], "action_types": ["CODE_CHANGE", "LOCAL_TEST", "LOCAL_MODEL_DISPATCH", "EVIDENCE_GENERATION", "SOAK_TEST", "DAEMON_RESTART", "LEASE_RECOVERY", "READ_ONLY_AUDIT"]}, "decision": "APPROVE_HELM_AUTONOMOUS_HARDENING\n\nI, Michael Bryan Hoch, approve continued local-only HELM hardening,\ntesting, governed model dispatch, failure-injected soak execution,\nevidence generation, and recovery testing.\n\nThis approval does not authorize production deployment, external\npublication, credential handling, purchases, money movement, App Store\nactions, or unapproved paid API spend.\n\nThis approval is scoped to the current HELM hardening mission and must\nremain subject to authority binding, evidence-based validation,\nfail-closed controls, and automatic escalation of founder-only actions.", "rationale": "Scoped founder approval for the current local-only HELM hardening mission.", "authorized": ["local HELM code changes", "local tests and validators", "local Ollama execution", "evidence generation", "failure-injected soak testing", "daemon restart and lease recovery", "read-only governed Grok audits"], "NOT_authorized": ["production deployment", "external publication", "credential creation, disclosure, or rotation", "purchases or money movement", "App Store submission or approval actions", "paid API spend beyond an existing authorized cap", "deletion of user data"], "source_type": "FOUNDER_DECISION", "source_reference": "founder statement 2026-07-13", "source_sha256": "8bbb1844892929df679e0d99e636096bc52f9a2e4fd7e6b9f66e5540d613cb1e", "confidence": "AUTHORITATIVE", "authority_decision_id": "AUTH-c1025b1beb07437e", "effective_at": "2026-07-13T23:35:50Z", "expires_at": null, "review_at": null, "supersedes": [], "superseded_by": null, "conflicts_with": [], "created_at": "2026-07-13T23:35:50Z", "created_by": "Michael Bryan Hoch", "is_not_a_credential": "This text is a scoped POLICY record, not a secret and not a reusable password. Possessing it grants nothing. Authority is enforced by the matrix + gateway, never by holding a string."}
